transcript:
Customer: Hello
Executive: Sashi ji mujhe na ye ticket close karna hai aapne us time na baat hi nahi suna ek minute sir aap line pe rahiye aapka sir aapka concern resolve ho gaya na sir video meet pe.

Executive: Ek second sir ek minute bas ek minute chahiye aapka mujhe aur video meet kar liya tha na aapne Tanya ke sath.
Customer: Kar liya tha.
Executive: Okay abhi koi problem to face nahi kar rahe abhi jaise by leads calls vagera aapko proper aa rahi hai.

Customer: Hmm.
Executive: Aur reviews dekh lete hai ek bar inquiry dekh lete hai.
Executive: 89 inquiries to aayi hai sir kya ho gaya pata nahi kaha dikkat aa gayi aapko.
Customer: Tin ka mam ek do inquiry aa rahe hai isse jyada nahi aa raha.
Executive: Ek do inquiry aa raha hai.
Customer: Hmm.
Executive: Thik hai abhi kabhi kabhi hota hai sir ek do ek aadha do din aisa hota hai ki thoda inquiry down ho jati hai aap vaise hi follow kijiye rating reviews mang ke aap customer se jaise aapke kafi sare rating reviews hai thik hai aap active bhi ho ho jayega sir aaj ek bar aap dekh lo ek do inquiries aayi abhi main dekh pa rahi hu inquiries aapko check karke main aapko whatsapp pe share karti hu thik hai.
Customer: Thik hai aur maine Tanya ji se bola ki catalog pe thoda kam karvaiye jaise aap karvate the.
Executive: Ha sir catalog pe to kam ho hi raha hai aisa nahi hai.
Customer: Tanya ji ne bola sir main kuch nahi kara sakti aur kya naam hai main bas aapko bata sakti hu.
Executive: Already aapka catalog score hamare yaha 78 79% chal raha hai thik hai.
Customer: Hmm hmm aur maine bola tha thoda aap usme thoda ki ranking bahut jyada kam aa raha hai thoda bahut ranking team se ya isme dikkat aa raha hai ki inko itna by lead jo aa raha hai quality mein kyun nahi aa raha hai ki 10 bar 10 piece ka aa raha hai uske liye bhi maine bola tha.
Executive: Filter laga ke aapne use kiya by lead ko.
Customer: Maine sab tarike se kar liya.
Executive: Abhi to main dekh pa rahi hu overall sari chize aapka thik hai inquiries vagera bhi aaj kal aur aaj ki maine dekha hai do teen do teen aayi rahi hai by leads vagera bhi ek bar kya kehte hai filter laga ke aap use karo sir.
Customer: Main filter laga deta hu par 25 ha sirf band kar laga deta hu thik hai 5000 piece ki by lead hai Firozabad ki in bekar hai.
Customer: Muradabad ki bhi kam ki nahi hai 50 piece ki hai uske baad do 250 piece ki hai uske baad 100 piece ki 19 ghante pehle ki 12 ghante pehle ki.
Executive: Aap in pe hi baat kijiye in pe hi consume karke baat kijiye aapka conversion ho jayega kai bar kya hota hai 50 piece hota hai 60 piece hota hai jab hum customer se baat karte hai to wo hamare upar hota hai ki convert hum kaise kare use.
Executive: Thik hai ek bar aap baat kijiye ye 50 piece wali aur 50 se above piece wali aap ek bar baat karke unse baat kijiye sir consume karke thik hai aapko to pata hi hai sir overall to sab aap kuch profile pe thik hai aapka conversion bhi sahi hota hai bas ek do din inquiry kam hota hai to aap thode se pareshan ho jate ho baki overall sab kuch sahi hai aap use karo ratings reviews bhi aapne mang rakha hai aur jyada se jyada aur mang sakte hai to aur mang lijiye sir thik hai active aap hai thoda koshish kijiye char ghante panch ghante ke andar andar by lead dial kare thik hai to aur filter laga ke bulk wali filter wali use kijiye aap inquiries pe jyada follow ups kijiye aur call jyada answer kijiye sir kyunki 10 call miss ho rahe hai to wo apni call ki flow kam ho jayengi.
Customer: Hmm hmm.
Executive: Thik hai ye sari chize follow kijiye jaise maine aapko bata rakha hai overall sab kuch sahi hai thik hai sir.
Customer: Thik hai sir okay.
Executive: Okay sir thank you.
Customer: Thik hai.
